{
  "version": 1,
  "_comment": "Canonical design tokens for CodeBurn. The Swift mac/ app reads this at build time to populate Theme.swift; the desktop/ Tauri frontend imports it as CSS custom properties. Side-by-side screenshots on macOS and Linux should read as the same product.",
